{"tid":2362384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺大流行各國封城致全球全年碳排放減 7%　無阻 2020 年成史上最熱年","createTime":"2021-01-11T11:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T12:08:31.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"70be33ab0dc67027d730c538a3e1567206941658","tid":2362384,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n雖然武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 大流行，各國出現封城而使全球碳排放量減少了 7％ ，但地球溫度仍達到了前所未有的水平。歐盟科學計劃哥白尼氣候變化服務(C3S) 上周五 (8/1) 確認， 2020 年是有記錄以來最熱一年，比前工業時代高 1.25&deg;C 。更重要是，過去一年並不似此前最熱年 2016 年一樣受厄爾尼諾現象 (El Nino) 所影響。<br />\n<br />\nC3S 的衛星數據顯示，去年某些地區的暖化幅度遠超過全球平均水平。歐洲的平均地表溫度比前工業時代高 2.2&deg;C，比 2019 年再高出近 0.5&deg;C ；北極地區的暖化程度最為嚴峻，西伯利亞北部和北極地區比 19 世紀中葉高出近 7&deg;C ，而西伯利亞地區的山火一直持續至去年秋天，向大氣釋出破紀錄的 25 億噸二氧化碳，相當於西班牙、埃及或越南的年度碳排放量，亦比 2019 年排放增加了三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/C3S_PR_Jan2021_Fig1_12month_anomaly_Global_ea_2t_202001-202012_ygZdh_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FC3S_PR_Jan2021_Fig1_12month_anomaly_Global_ea_2t_202001-202012_ygZdh_1200x0.png&h=a328aba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit: C3S<br />\n<br />\nC3S 總監 Carlo Buontempo 表示， 2020 年的異常溫暖令人觸目，這亦再次提醒人們必須大幅減排碳，以防止將來出現的嚴重氣候破壞。<br />\nC3S 又指連同 2020 年，自 2015 年起的 6 年都是有記錄以來最熱 6 年；最近 21 年中也有 20 年打破或平了最熱年記錄，表明暖化趨勢持續不斷並在加劇。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/武肺大流行各國封城致全球全年碳排放減-7-無阻-2020-年成史上最熱年/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%E6%AD%A6%E8%82%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E8%87%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E7%A2%B3%E6%8E%92%E6%94%BE%E6%B8%9B-7-%E7%84%A1%E9%98%BB-2020-%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E7%86%B1%E5%B9%B4%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=fb7401f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%E6%AD%A6%E8%82%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E8%87%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E7%A2%B3%E6%8E%92%E6%94%BE%E6%B8%9B-7-%E7%84%A1%E9%98%BB-2020-%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E7%86%B1%E5%B9%B4%2F&h=2a0a45b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/武肺大流行各國封城致全球全年碳排放減-7-無阻-2020-年成史上最熱年/</a>"},{"pid":"49deebe64f3afdf7d3779f2bf789e53cb6c78d39","tid":2362384,"uid":13303,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"專家食屎啦.jpg"},{"pid":"9821afdaffb898443be998fb1fa9a1b986fcc5c5","tid":2362384,"uid":37197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"睇埋今年就知<br />\n如果都係繼續熱 證明碳排放唔係導致全球暖化主因<br />\n可能真係地球既cycle"},{"pid":"b8ba0d4fde0be34ef2d9eed30d46942667844bc2","tid":2362384,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9821afdaffb898443be998fb1fa9a1b986fcc5c5","tid":2362384,"uid":37197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"睇埋今年就知<br />\n如果都係繼續熱 證明碳排放唔係導致全球暖化主因<br />\n可能真係地球既cycle"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:54:00.000Z","msg":"你識唔識㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲滯現象"},{"pid":"a3dfa05a3636a2393471a050c4cbd46590943821","tid":2362384,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"鄰國成日話自己一早走出疫情丫嘛，你地全世界都減緊但係鄰國仲排緊囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a592d47812d03f6fe68db12c5119b9364a49ca51","tid":2362384,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9821afdaffb898443be998fb1fa9a1b986fcc5c5","tid":2362384,"uid":37197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"睇埋今年就知<br />\n如果都係繼續熱 證明碳排放唔係導致全球暖